# Trivy ignore list for the lama-sidecar image scans (CI and release).
#
# One CVE ID per line, with a comment on the line above stating the
# reachability rationale (why the vulnerable code path cannot be hit in this
# image) — per the block-on-unreviewed-HIGH policy, an entry without a
# rationale counts as unreviewed and must be removed.
#
# Example:
# # only exploitable via feature X; not installed/enabled in this image
# CVE-2099-12345
